      "content": "it's not just \"heavy\" though. it feels permanent. like i've made mistakes that can't be fixed. no matter how much i work or how much i try to save, the numbers just keep going the wrong way. it feels like i'm just running in place while the walls close in. i can't see a single version of the future where this isn't just a constant, suffocating cycle.",
